I'm now integrating the preloader. I'll make the preloader fade out instead of unmounting it to ensure a smoother transition. I've decided to import the `Preloader` into `Hero.tsx` to handle the logic there. I'll set the z-index of the preloader to 100 to ensure it covers the `NavBar`. I will also create `components/Preloader.tsx`. The Preloader will display "GRAIN."


