Now, I'm aiming to refine the logic for preloader display and hiding. My current implementation involves a state variable `videoLoaded` and a progress variable. The preloader transitions out upon video loading completion. I'm exploring adding a small delay, post-loading, before fading out the preloader for a more polished effect. I'll make sure the user can see progress up to 100%, and can have a smooth loading experience.


