I'm now implementing the visuals of the preloader. The code uses flexbox for the layout, centered content with a dark background. The logo "GRAIN" is styled with a large font, bold weight, and tracking. I've added a progress bar with a white background and a colored, glowing fill. The percentage is also displayed. I'll make the transition smooth, with the loading percentage updated as the video loads.


