I'm now simplifying the preloader state further. I've consolidated state management to minimize complexity. The loading status will handle visibility and transition, and I'll use a single state variable. I'll refactor the event listeners in `Hero.tsx` to align with the new state management approach, aiming for a cleaner implementation.


