I'm now streamlining the preloader integration. I am simplifying state management, using a single `isLoading` state variable to manage both visibility and transition of the preloader. I've refactored the component to use a `progress` variable and update event listeners to use a single timer, to avoid complexity. I'm focusing on a smoother, clearer preloader experience.

